description: Время указано во временной зоне сервера (для получения Московского времени нужно отнять 3 часа)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT max(date) as update_date,SUM(`count`) as key_id_count
FROM (
	(SELECT   toDate(x.`datetime`) as `date`, COUNT(x.key_id)  as `count`
		FROM DataCore.rmq_log x
		WHERE x.`table` = 'terminals_capacity'  AND x.is_success = TRUE 
		GROUP BY  x.key_id, x.`datetime`)
	) z_q  
GROUP BY date 
ORDER BY 1 DESC 
LIMIT 10
